Package: grabsampling
Type: Package
Title: Probability of detection for grab sample selection
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
          person("Mayooran","Thevaraja", email = "mayooran@eng.jfn.ac.lk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
